OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1773083488
OL,3,CFirm responsible for 'Your Island
OL,4,CPension' liable for misconduct
OL,6,FThe pension provider responsible for
OL,7,Fmanaging Guernsey's government-backed
OL,8,Fsecondary pension scheme has been
OL,9,Ffound guilty of wilful misconduct in
OL,10,Frelation to another fund.
OL,12,FYour Island Pension (YIP) is
OL,13,Fadministered by the Sovereign Trust,
OL,14,Fwhich is currently being sued for more
OL,15,Fthan $25 million by a group of
OL,16,Fdisabled pilots.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1773083488
OL,3,CFirm responsible for 'Your Island
OL,4,CPension' liable for misconduct
OL,6,FThe group of 25 said the firm
OL,7,Fmismanaged their money, which was held
OL,8,Fin a trust designed as a safety net
OL,9,Ffor those who cannot fly after losing
OL,10,Fmedical certificates.
OL,12,FA court has since found in favour of
OL,13,Fthe pilots and that the mismanagement
OL,14,Fof their fund led to its collapse and
OL,15,Fthe pilots being denied benefits.
OL,17,FWhen secondary pensions became a legal
OL,18,Fobligation for employers to provide,
OL,19,Fthe States of Guernsey promoted YIP,
OL,20,Fand more than 4,000 people have signed
OL,21,Fup so far.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1773083488
OL,3,CFirm responsible for 'Your Island
OL,4,CPension' liable for misconduct
OL,6,FSovereign Trust was chosen to manage
OL,7,Fthe scheme, but does not hold the
OL,8,Fmoney.
OL,10,FDespite this, following the ruling
OL,11,Fread out in court last month, the
OL,12,Fgovernment now says it is "determined
OL,13,Fto ensure that all pensions" managed
OL,14,Fby the firm are secure.
OL,16,FThe Committee for Employment & Social
OL,17,FSecurity is closely monitoring the
OL,18,Fsituation, as it essentially partnered
OL,19,Fwith Sovereign to provide the state-
OL,20,Fsanctioned secondary pension.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1773083488
OL,3,CFirm responsible for 'Your Island
OL,4,CPension' liable for misconduct
OL,6,FTina Bury, President of the Committee
OL,7,Ffor Employment & Social Security,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Sovereign Trust (Guernsey)
OL,9,FLimited, part of the wider Sovereign
OL,10,FGroup, was appointed some years ago to
OL,11,Flead the Your Island Pension Scheme
OL,12,Fwhich was established at the direction
OL,13,Fof the States to ensure all islanders
OL,14,Fhave access to a pension through work.
OL,26,@pD@GOU
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1773083488
OL,3,CFirm responsible for 'Your Island
OL,4,CPension' liable for misconduct
OL,6,F"The Committee has been made aware of
OL,7,Fthe court action, which is now nearing
OL,8,Fits conclusion; and while it would be
OL,9,Finappropriate to comment on any
OL,10,Fimplications at this stage, I can
OL,11,Fconfirm we will be considering the
OL,12,Ffinal judgment in detail."
OL,14,FThe Committee confirmed it would be
OL,15,F"assessing the implications" of the
OL,16,Fcourt ruling. The full judgment and
OL,17,Fany potential compensation have not
OL,18,Fbeen published yet.
OL,26,@tD@ZO]
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1773083488
OL,3,CFirm responsible for 'Your Island
OL,4,CPension' liable for misconduct
OL,6,FSovereign wouldn't comment on the
OL,7,Fgovernment's concerns, but did provide
OL,8,Fthe following statement:
OL,10,F"The Royal Court has issued a partial
OL,11,Fdecision. Whilst we are disappointed
OL,12,Fwith the Royal Court's conclusions to
OL,13,Fdate and mischaracterisations
OL,14,Fcontained in press reports, it is
OL,15,Fappropriate to await the Court's full
OL,16,Fjudgment before commenting further on
OL,17,Fthe outcome or any next steps that
OL,18,FSovereign may take in the proceedings.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/8
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,388,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F387A1773083488
OL,3,CFirm responsible for 'Your Island
OL,4,CPension' liable for misconduct
OL,6,F"Sovereign did not establish the
OL,7,Finitial pilot's income protection
OL,8,Fscheme but took over the
OL,9,Fadministration of that scheme in 2015.
OL,11,F"Sovereign wishes to reassure clients
OL,12,Fand intermediaries that this will not
OL,13,Fhave any direct impact on its
OL,14,Fbusiness, including its management of
OL,15,FYour Island Pension."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/8
